728369f-c.title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Woodrow Road
728369f-c.text:
1281 Arthur Kill Road, north side, west of
Woodrow Road, showing the home and barns of Wms

views.

728368f-a.title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Woodrow Road
728368f-a.text:
1260 Arthur K1ll Road, adjoining the S.W. corner
of Woodrow Road. This house belonged to Dr. D. A. Edgar
in 1874, and later (1898) to David J. Tysen. In 1907
it was owned by Wm. Fitzgerald and in 1917 by David J.
Tysen. The dates refer to maps on which the names of the
owners are recorded.
April 9, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO RPRODUCTIONS
728368f-a.folder: Arthur Kill Road & Woodrow Road, Staten Island, NY

729959f-a.title: Richmond: Woodrow Road - Arthur Kill Road
729959f-a.text:
(1)
Woodrow Road, east side, 800 feet south of Arthur
Kill Road, showing the D. V. H. Floyd House (Butlere 1853 map).
From 1874 to 1898 the maps show it to have been the H. Barger
house, and from 1907 to 1917 the Dierauf house. This is the
north side of the dwelling.
April 9, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO RCPRODUCTIONS
(2)
Looking north and showing the south side of
the house.
April 9, 1927
P. L. Sperr
NO RERODUCTIONS
